verses.roman:
jaya jaya śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya gauracandra
jayādvaitacandra jaya jaya nityānanda

synonyms: jaya jaya—all glories; śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya—Lord Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; gaura-candra—Lord Gauracandra; jaya ādvaita-candra—all glories to Advaita Ācārya; jaya jaya—all glories to; nityānanda—Lord Nityānanda Prabhu.
translation: All glories to Śrī Kṛṣṇa Caitanya Mahāprabhu! All glories to Advaitacandra! All glories to Lord Nityānanda Prabhu!
